     <p>Text styles</p>
     <pre>
*This text will be italic*
_This will also be italic_
**This text will be bold**
__This will also be bold__

*You **can** combine them*
</pre>
    </div>
    <div class="col">
      <h3>Lists</h3>
      <p>Unordered</p>
      <pre>
* Item 1
* Item 2
  * Item 2a
  * Item 2b</pre>
     <p>Ordered</p>
     <pre>
1. Item 1
2. Item 2
3. Item 3
   * Item 3a
   * Item 3b</pre>
    </div>
